122 /*========== Test Cases =====================================================*/
123 void testCAN_TxStateEstimationCharging(void) {
124  CAN_MESSAGE_PROPERTIES_s testMessage = {
125  .id = CANTX_PACK_STATE_ESTIMATION_ID,
126  .idType = CANTX_PACK_STATE_ESTIMATION_ID_TYPE,
127  .dlc = 8u,
128  .endianness = CANTX_PACK_STATE_ESTIMATION_ENDIANNESS,
129  };
130  uint8_t data[8] = {0};
131 
132  for (uint8_t s = 0u; s < BS_NR_OF_STRINGS; s++) {
133  can_kShim.pTableSox->minimumSoc_perc[s] = 71.2f;
134  can_kShim.pTableSox->maximumSoc_perc[s] = 74.2f;
135  can_kShim.pTableSox->minimumSoe_perc[s] = 74.6f;
136  can_kShim.pTableSox->maximumSoe_perc[s] = 78.1f;
137  can_kShim.pTableSox->minimumSoe_Wh[s] = 19200 / BS_NR_OF_STRINGS;
138  }
139 
140  DATA_Read1DataBlock_IgnoreAndReturn(0u);
141  /* System is currently charging */
142  BMS_GetBatterySystemState_IgnoreAndReturn(BMS_CHARGING);
143  /* All strings connected */
144  for (uint8_t s = 0; s < BS_NR_OF_STRINGS; s++) {
145  BMS_IsStringClosed_IgnoreAndReturn(true);
146  }
147  BMS_GetNumberOfConnectedStrings_IgnoreAndReturn(BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
148  BMS_GetBatterySystemState_IgnoreAndReturn(BMS_CHARGING);
149  BMS_GetNumberOfConnectedStrings_IgnoreAndReturn(BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
150  BMS_GetNumberOfConnectedStrings_IgnoreAndReturn(BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
151  BMS_GetNumberOfConnectedStrings_IgnoreAndReturn(BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
152 
153  CANTX_PackStateEstimation(testMessage, data, NULL_PTR, &can_kShim);
154 
155  /** Values of:
156  * pack SOC: 74.2%
157  * pack SOE: 78.1%
158  * pack Energy: 19.2kWh
159  * pack SOH: 100.0%
160  */
161  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0x73, data[0]);
162  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0xED, data[1]);
163  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0xE8, data[2]);
164  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0x2F, data[3]);
165  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0xA0, data[4]);
166  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0x00, data[5]);
167  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0x07, data[6]);
168  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0x80, data[7]);
169 }
170 
171 void testCAN_TxStateEstimationDischarging(void) {
172  CAN_MESSAGE_PROPERTIES_s testMessage = {
173  .id = CANTX_PACK_STATE_ESTIMATION_ID,
174  .idType = CANTX_PACK_STATE_ESTIMATION_ID_TYPE,
175  .dlc = 8u,
176  .endianness = CANTX_PACK_STATE_ESTIMATION_ENDIANNESS,
177  };
178 
179  uint8_t data[8] = {0};
180 
181  for (uint8_t s = 0u; s < BS_NR_OF_STRINGS; s++) {
182  can_kShim.pTableSox->minimumSoc_perc[s] = 74.2f;
183  can_kShim.pTableSox->maximumSoc_perc[s] = 78.2f;
184  can_kShim.pTableSox->minimumSoe_perc[s] = 78.1f;
185  can_kShim.pTableSox->maximumSoe_perc[s] = 83.1f;
186  can_kShim.pTableSox->minimumSoe_Wh[s] = 19200 / BS_NR_OF_STRINGS;
187  }
188 
189  DATA_Read1DataBlock_IgnoreAndReturn(0u);
190  /* System is currently charging */
191  BMS_GetBatterySystemState_IgnoreAndReturn(BMS_DISCHARGING);
192  /* All strings connected */
193  for (uint8_t s = 0; s < BS_NR_OF_STRINGS; s++) {
194  BMS_IsStringClosed_IgnoreAndReturn(true);
195  }
196  BMS_GetNumberOfConnectedStrings_IgnoreAndReturn(BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
197  BMS_GetBatterySystemState_IgnoreAndReturn(BMS_DISCHARGING);
198  BMS_GetNumberOfConnectedStrings_IgnoreAndReturn(BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
199  BMS_GetNumberOfConnectedStrings_IgnoreAndReturn(BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
200  BMS_GetNumberOfConnectedStrings_IgnoreAndReturn(BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
201 
202  CANTX_PackStateEstimation(testMessage, data, NULL_PTR, &can_kShim);
203 
204  /** Values of:
205  * pack SOC: 74.2%
206  * pack SOE: 78.1%
207  * pack Energy: 19.2kWh
208  * pack SOH: 100.0%
209  */
210  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0x73, data[0]);
211  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0xED, data[1]);
212  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0xE8, data[2]);
213  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0x2F, data[3]);
214  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0xA0, data[4]);
215  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0x00, data[5]);
216  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0x07, data[6]);
217  TEST_ASSERT_EQUAL(0x80, data[7]);
218 }
